Cell["\<\
Now we plot a bar chart comparing the current population with the population \
in 1950:\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.787572577486886*^9, 
  3.787572614040958*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"991aa6f9-4314-4dd2-9b2a-\
24855a71841c"],

