Cell["\<\
A stacked bar chart consisting of a single bar is useful when you want to \
depict how some quantity is made up of sub-quantities. To exemplify this, \
here is some data on the current composition of the UK\[CloseCurlyQuote]s \
House of Commons:\
\>", "Text",
