Cell["\<\
This does not look very good! The axis labels are getting in the way, making \
the plots hard to read. One solution is to get rid of the axes altogether:\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.787653575703603*^9, 
  3.7876536261377707`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"9b5d6340-cd20-4fb5-bbcf-\
