Cell["\<\
The sequence of points is usually shown by connecting the data points by a \
line (hence the term \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]line \
plot\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]). You could also show the symbols to emphasize \
where the data points are:\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7878375455783143`*^9, 3.787837605587229*^9}, {
  3.787841549494649*^9, 
  3.787841576782346*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"29b39031-9ac0-45c6-85d8-\
82ff5d92ec6a"],

